{"_id":"PA124qk1USkJvC89","name":"3D Canvas WIKI","content":"<p style=\"text-align:center\">The 3D Canvas Documentation has been moved to a Wiki</p>\n<p style=\"width:100%;text-align:center\"><a style=\"box-shadow:inset 0px 1px 0px 0px #f9eca0;background:linear-gradient(to bottom, #f0c911 5%, #f2ab1e 100%);background-color:#f0c911;border-radius:1px;border:1px solid #e65f44;display:inline-block;cursor:pointer;color:#c92200;font-family:Arial;font-size:36px;font-weight:bold;padding:6px 24px;text-decoration:none;text-shadow:0px 1px 0px #ded17c\" href=\"https://github.com/theripper93/canvas3dcompendium/wiki\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Open the WIKI</a></p>","img":"icons/sundries/books/book-red-exclamation.webp","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"WxrhraieeJZ8WIty":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"JournalEntry.UPXEDA7SEcpRr0jc"}}}
{"_id":"t18ycwap0yp6ABYV","name":"Create a Skybox","content":"<h2>Step 1 - Create Skybox</h2>\n<p>Create your skybox, when happy, click the download skybox button, 1K is suggested - Do not use 4K.</p>\n<p>Once downloaded, unzip into a folder.</p>\n<p><iframe title src=\"https://tools.wwwtyro.net/space-3d/index.html\" width=\"100%\" height=\"700\"></iframe></p>\n<h2>Step 2 - Convert</h2>\n<p>Select 6 separate images as the Cubemap Format (the icon with 6 Squares in a 3x2 Grid).</p>\n<p>Click chose files, select the files in the folder you previously downloaded (all 6) and confirm.</p>\n<p>Wait a couple seconds and you will be prompted to download your skybox.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><iframe title src=\"https://360toolkit.co/convert-cubemap-to-spherical-equirectangular\" width=\"100%\" height=\"700\"></iframe></p>\n<h2>Step 3 - Use in 3D Canvas</h2>\n<p>In your scene configuration, use the file you just downloaded in your HDRI Field, remove the file present in the Skybox field (by deleting the text)</p>","img":"icons/environment/settlement/graveyard-tombstone-night.webp","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"Cspu3pxFr7tu7SU7":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"JournalEntry.5ZSwx5fXCekU4iHy"}}}
